<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM13">
<l>niṉaiyā toḻitikaṇ ṭāyneñca mēyiṅkōr tañcameṉṟu</l>
<l>maṉaiyā ḷaiyummakka ṭammaiyun tēṟiyō rāṟupukku</l>
<l>naṉaiyāc caṭaimuṭi nampaṉṉan tātainon tātacentī</l>
<l>yaṉaiyā ṉamarar pirāṉaṇṭa vāṇa ṉaṭittalamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Stop not thinking, look, heart, as a refuge here,</l>
<l>after having trusted in wife and children, the place at the feet of the lord</l>
<l>with a crown of matted hair that does not become wet as a river enters [it],</l> 
<l>our father, he who is like imperishable red fire, lord of the celestials, resident of the universe.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
